@node "Thanx" "Fireball would like to thank and greet..."

 @{fg shine}<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<@{fg text}
 Fireball sucks ?  Aussagekräftige Beschwerden bitte an eine
 der folgenden Personen, die mitunter schuldig zu sprechen sind
 für den leibhaftig gewordenen Fluch namens """"Fireball""""" ! ;-)
 @{fg shadow}>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>@{fg text}

 @{bg shine}Team-Fireball thanX *in no stupid order* :@{bg back}
 Bernd H*]˘# (one you can trust of) ; even so Dr.HC.Frankenstone (da
 right hand of da gucky :-)) and the Webjump Crew (haaarghh
 meckersoft) ; Roman Bujna ("these unholy bastards!") ; Frank
 Kammerewert (for not gettin` tired of picpicpixeling) ; Stamen (for his
 great ami-mods) ; Mela Preus (dark,darker,darkest witch;-=) ; Kilian
 Servais (the metal-warrior for his hmc in da feiabohl) ;
 Andreas Magerl (the amiga-guru for da af-link and for support in
 any way) ; Carsten Schröder (for his great AmAktuell) ; Petra
 Struck (anews rulezz!!!!) ; Bernhard Murmann (the murmel some thanX
 for uploading feiabohl) ; Jessy Zagolla (mrs. allround in her element) ;
 Chris Krüger (incredible supporting feiabohl - even without an
 amiga !ha!) ; all this nice Webmasters around Ami-Globe, who "linked"
 us on their pages - and thanX to all the other guys `n girls who
 believed in us and supported us in any way. We`re back to
 attack - and without you this would definitly not possible. Hail the
 holy underground !

 @{bg shine}Our greets:@{bg back}
 to all our families, our friends, saufkumpanen, headbangers,
 big brothers, latin lovers, and groupies inside and outside
 germany ;-), in fact: Chrissy Verfürden (dr.holland),
 Jenny Leohard ("i don`t give a fuxx, i`ll just make it"), Stefanie
 Krewe (once again flower power), Jhonny Smith (you won`t read that,
 guy ! So in that case we could send you some terrible notes! haaa!),
 Brian Austin (www.whatareonlinemagsfor?), Ben Koch (judas `n peace be
 my guide), Siggi (and his headbanging kalei;by moonlight into glory
 ride), the "Night Owl" (drums,sex and pure metal:-)), da "Delax" on pc-
 kaputt (and the rest,the rare,the unholy shit on channel chatcity;-)),
 "Freakx" ("isn`t that some kind of revelation or revolution?")
 and "Sensibar" (without sword in hand) - we`ll never forget that cruel
 night with burnin` eyes ;-), the armies of the night on www.manowar.com
 (and of course,the one,the hell of a webmaster;-)), Mr. Arjen
 ;Remember Forever; Lucassen (you`re so damn cool,guy! hail!  ;-)),
 "Sand29w" and "Guilovine" on chat.de (who finally found their meaning
 of life, after the "very hot" meeting in da slippery cage..;=)),
 and krits tu ohl the...
 other freaks we`ve met inside and outside the net. Special greet to all
 our new and forthcoming members (without your faith this fire won`t
 hold for very long) and to YOU (read it,spread it ;-)), to
 Tyschtschenko (be gone,be brave), to the other OnlineMags who
 will keep the fire burning (and those who not do: &%¶˘ you and your
 lame point of view! death to the false ones!) and... finally fin!
 may peace prevail on mother earth.

 @{b}Team-Fireball@{ub}

